## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent legal changes post-October 2023. The complexity of abortion laws, which vary significantly by jurisdiction, means that this report provides a general overview rather than an exhaustive legal analysis. Additionally, cultural and religious factors influencing abortion laws were not deeply explored in this report.

